Package: gaitkit
Type: Package
Title: Universal Gait Event Detection Toolkit for 'R'
Version: 1.2.3
Authors@R: person("Frederic", "Fer",
    email = "f.fer@institut-myologie.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Detect heel-strike and toe-off events from motion capture data
    using 10 validated methods ('BIKE', 'Zeni', 'OConnor', 'Hreljac',
    'Mickelborough', 'Ghoussayni', 'Vancanneyt', 'DGEI', 'IntellEvent',
    'DeepEvent'). Includes ensemble voting, gait cycle extraction, and
    publication-ready visualisation. Uses a C-accelerated 'Python' backend
    accessed through 'reticulate' from 'R'. Method references include
    O'Connor et al. (2007) <doi:10.1016/j.gaitpost.2006.05.016> and
    Zeni et al. (2008) <doi:10.1016/j.gaitpost.2007.07.007>. Additional
    implementations are documented at
    <https://github.com/IDMDataHub/gaitkit>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/IDMDataHub/gaitkit
BugReports: https://github.com/IDMDataHub/gaitkit/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    reticulate (>= 1.28)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
